<article lang="en-US"><sect1><title>Hbox</title>
<para>The hbox component is used to create a horizontally oriented box. Each component placed in the hbox will be placed horizontally in a row.</para>
<para/>
<para>
<inlinegraphic fileref="images/box.png" width="4.047cm"/>
</para>
<title/>
